//Youtube
div(class="youtube-most-popular")
	div(class="form-group")
		label(class="label-control warning") Maximum number of videos
			span(class="warningText") Careful! The default quota allocation is 10,000 units per day. Every 50 videos counts as 1 units.
		div(class="range range-node")
			input(type="range" min="50" max="10000" value="100" step="50" id="youtube-most-popular-count" onchange="ytMostPoprangeNode.value=value")
			output(id="ytMostPoprangeNode") 100
	div(class="form-group")
		label Localized Language
		input(class="form-control", id="ytHl", placeholder="e.g. ISO 639-1")
	div(class="form-group")
		label(for="ytVideoCategoryId") Video Category ID
		input(class="form-control", id="ytVideoCategoryId", placeholder="e.g., 1=Film & Animation, 10=Music, 17=Sports")
		small(class="form-text text-muted")
			| Enter the category ID for the type of videos you wish to filter by.
			ul
				li 1 = Film & Animation
				li 10 = Music
				li 24 = Entertainment
				li 25 = News & Politics
			| For a complete list of category IDs, refer to the this <a href="https://gist.github.com/dgp/1b24bf2961521bd75d6c" target="_blank">documentation</a>.

